Package: paramlink2
Type: Package
Title: Parametric Linkage Analysis
Version: 0.9.9000
Authors@R: person("Magnus Dehli", "Vigeland", 
                  email = "m.d.vigeland@medisin.uio.no", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9134-4962"))
Description: Parametric linkage analysis of monogenic traits in medical 
    pedigrees. Features include singlepoint analysis, multipoint analysis via 
    'MERLIN' (Abecasis et al. (2002) <doi:10.1038/ng786>), visualisation of LOD 
    scores and summaries of linkage peaks. Disease models may be specified to 
    accomodate phenocopies, reduced penetrance and liability classes. 
    'paramlink2' is part of the 'ped suite' ecosystem, presented in 
    'Pedigree Analysis in R' (Vigeland, 2021, ISBN:9780128244302).
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/magnusdv/paramlink2
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-GB
LazyData: true
